ng Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.999779446841637, \"rank\": 0.00017101796600705577, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports Scene\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"The start\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 268}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"the final preparations\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"the newly-announced flagbearers\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the first time in history, the Opening Ceremony for the Summer Olympics will not take place inside a main stadium, but in full view of the public on the River Seine.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 484}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening Ceremony\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"a main stadium\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"full view\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 6,000 to 7,000 athletes, and several thousand more coaches and other delegation members, will sail down the Seine on 85 barges and boats.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999903891421, \"rank\": 9.470461257337905e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Around 6,000 to 7,000 athletes\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"several thousand more coaches\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"other delegation members\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"85 barges\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As many as 300,000 spectators are set to watch the parade from temporary stands and along the river banks, with an additional 200,000 poised to do likewise from apartments overlooking the area.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"As many as 300,000 spectators\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"the parade\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary stands\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"the river banks\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"apartments\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Table tennis superstar Ma Long and artistic swimming team captain Feng Yu will carry the flag for China at the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ma_Long\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ma Long\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13382519\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ma_Long\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ma_Long\"}, {\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.o